======================================================================
CHI ANALYSIS: SIGN PATTERN
======================================================================

  For circulant tournaments on Z_n:
  chi > 0 means more even-dim homology; chi < 0 means more odd-dim

  Interval n=3: chi=+0, chi/n=+0, (n-1)/2=1
  Interval n=5: chi=+0, chi/n=+0, (n-1)/2=2
  Interval n=7: chi=-7, chi/n=-1, (n-1)/2=3
  Interval n=9: chi=+9, chi/n=+1, (n-1)/2=4

  Paley p=3: chi=+0, chi/p=+0
  Paley p=7: chi=+7, chi/p=+1

